---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	lang="en"
	title="Cookies — Gandía, summer 2026"
	description="About the cookies on this site. Short version: just Google Analytics to count visits, plus technical cookies from Netlify. No advertising and no marketing trackers."
	otherLangHref="/es/cookies/"
	otherLangLabel="Español"
>
	<p class="eyebrow">Cookies</p>
	<h1>About our <span class="accent">cookies</span></h1>
	<p class="tagline">
		Short version: just analytics to count visits — no advertising.
	</p>

	<h2>Analytics</h2>
	<p>
		We use <strong>Google Analytics</strong> to see how many people visit and which pages are popular. It sets cookies (names beginning with <strong>_ga</strong>) and sends Google information such as the pages you view, your approximate location (derived from your IP address) and your device and browser. We use this <strong>only for aggregate visitor statistics</strong> — never for advertising, and we don't sell or share it.
	</p>

	<h2>Technical</h2>
	<p>
		You may also encounter <strong>technical cookies</strong> set by <a href="https://www.netlify.com/" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Netlify</a>, the platform that hosts the site, for security and load balancing. They're required to deliver the site to your browser and don't track you across other sites.
	</p>
	<p>
		That's it — <strong>no advertising cookies and no marketing trackers</strong>. No Facebook Pixel, no ad tags.
	</p>

	<h2>If you'd rather opt out</h2>
	<p>
		Block cookies in your browser's settings or use private/incognito mode — the site will still work normally. To opt out of Google Analytics specifically, you can install Google's <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" rel="noopener" target="_blank">opt-out browser add-on</a>.
	</p>

	<p class="signoff">Questions? <a href="/contact/">Get in touch.</a></p>

	<style>
		h2 {
			font-family: Georgia, "Times New Roman", serif;
			font-size: 1.4rem;
			font-weight: 700;
			margin: 2.2rem 0 0.7rem;
			letter-spacing: -0.01em;
			color: var(--ink);
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
